that this was something

00:15:41.200 --> 00:15:42.700
that she wanted to
have in her life,

00:15:42.700 --> 00:15:46.210
and for the community,
which was great.

00:15:46.210 --> 00:15:50.260
And so now, with the book, I
am reaching a whole different

00:15:50.260 --> 00:15:53.020
category of people who--

00:15:53.020 --> 00:15:55.210
it's interesting what
kind of reaction.

00:15:55.210 --> 00:15:58.162
