bothering me all day long,

00:20:03.330 --> 00:20:07.680
or a work issue that I haven't
had time to sort of really

00:20:07.680 --> 00:20:08.520
drive into.

00:20:08.520 --> 00:20:12.690
So I've had to rethink what
productivity actually means.

00:20:12.690 --> 00:20:13.830
