00:20:27.630 --> 00:20:30.810
which is to reset the
expectations of the people who

00:20:30.810 --> 00:20:32.700
are hoping to hear
from you, right,

00:20:32.700 --> 00:20:35.100
because I think that's the
other thing that we've found,

00:20:35.100 --> 00:20:37.620
is that when we're waiting in
line for coffee, you're like,

00:20:37.620 --> 00:20:40.430
oh, this is an opportunity--
these two minutes--

00:20:40.430 --> 00:20:42.690
are an opportunity
to show my spouse

00:20:42.690 --> 00:20:44.910
how I'm thinking of them,
or that I'm on top of,

00:20:44.910 --> 00:20:47.700
like, you know, what's for
dinner, or my coworkers,

00:20:47.700 --> 00:20:51.750
that I know that we
needed to follow up on x--

00:20:51.750 --> 00:20:54.030
so resetting
expectations by setting

00:20:54.030 --> 00:20:57.300
outgoing messages, which I
think a lot of people don't do.

00:20:57.300 --> 00:20:59.130
And so I tell people,
like, you know,

00:20:59.130 --> 00:21:02.730
