00:21:10.980 --> 00:21:13.705
And I'm like, OK, so you have
a stomach virus for one hour,

00:21:13.705 --> 00:21:14.580
you know what I mean?

00:21:14.580 --> 00:21:17.470
Like, do what you've got to do,
because it's really important.

00:21:17.470 --> 00:21:19.136
But then, the other
thing that I've done

00:21:19.136 --> 00:21:22.650
is I joined a silent workspace,
where there's no talking.

00:21:22.650 --> 00:21:25.320
There's no eating, so no
crinkle, crinkle with, like--

00:21:25.320 --> 00:21:27.670
I love my snacks,
but none of that.

00:21:27.670 --> 00:21:30.480
And for me, like, I've realized
the most important work

00:21:30.480 --> 00:21:33.030
I do every week is
my writing, right?

00:21:33.030 --> 00:21:35.910
And I know that I need
that three to four hours.

00:21:35.910 --> 00:21:37.650
I've tried to write
the show in less,

00:21:37.650 --> 00:21:40.530
or I've tried to do it while I'm
jumping in and out of meetings.

00:21:40.530 --> 00:21:41.790
It doesn't work.

00:21:41.790 --> 00:21:43.800
I need the three to four hours.

00:21:43.800 --> 00:21:45.390
And so, I joined this workspace.

00:21:45.390 --> 00:21:48.640
I don't get there more than,
like, once or twice a week.

00:21:48.640 --> 00:21:50.520
But I think it's
worth it for me.

