00:28:08.870 --> 00:28:10.510
But then there's
the wonderful kind,

00:28:10.510 --> 00:28:12.560
which is positive
constructive mind wandering.

00:28:12.560 --> 00:28:14.320
This was Jerome
Singer, who did some

00:28:14.320 --> 00:28:18.580
of the most deep pioneering
work on mind wandering.

00:28:18.580 --> 00:28:21.340
And that is when we start to
do that wonderful constructive

00:28:21.340 --> 00:28:23.800
type of mind wandering.

