Anybody thinks that--
I mean, I really

00:32:30.480 --> 00:32:32.280
want to know, like, do you
think this is total bullshit?

00:32:32.280 --> 00:32:33.480
Like, I really, really--

00:32:33.480 --> 00:32:34.170
[LAUGHTER]

00:32:34.170 --> 00:32:37.860
--like, I'm really open to it,
because I think-- you know,

00:32:37.860 --> 00:32:39.850
I was at Powell's last
night in Portland.

00:32:39.850 --> 00:32:41.970
And I was like, oh, I'm
going to Google tomorrow.

00:32:41.970 --> 00:32:44.742
